<h2 id="expressions">Expressions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>One of the German mastiffs, maddened by a sudden attack of rabies, had torn to pieces every animal of any kind that <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="crossed its path"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(经过他所到之处)</code></b>, until the gardener from the house next door found the courage to face him and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="hack him to pieces"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(剁成肉酱)</code></b> with his machete.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Perhaps she would eventually have lost all hope of ever seeing an animal in the house again if it had not been for the thieves who, early one morning, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="forced"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(撬开/砸开)</code></b> a bathroom window and made off with the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="silver service"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(银餐具)</code></b> that had been in the family for five generations.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>But he opposed the purchase of a fierce dog, vaccinated or unvaccinated, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="running loose"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(放养)</code></b> or <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="chained up"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(拴起来)</code></b>, even if thieves were to steal everything he owned.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Fermina Daza, whose <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="straightforward character"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(直爽的性格)</code></b> had become more subtle with the years, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="seized on her husband's casual words"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(揪住丈夫用词的疏漏不放)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>That was how the local firemen learned to <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="render"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(提供/给予)</code></b> other emergency services, such as <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="forcing locks"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(撬开门锁)</code></b> or killing poisonous snakes, and the Medical School offered them a special course in first aid for minor accidents.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>But it suited her figure – <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="long-boned"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(身材修长)</code></b> and still slender and erect, her resilient hands without a single <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="age spot"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(老年斑)</code></b>, her steel-blue hair bobbed on a slant at her cheek.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

